I need to find the Login as Customer Log to review customer impersonation history. I've already checked the System menu and navigated to Bulk Actions Log, but that's not what I'm looking for. 

Looking at the accessibility tree more carefully, I don't see a direct link to 'Login as Customer Log' under the Action Logs section. The only visible option is 'Bulk Actions'.

In Magento, customer impersonation logs are typically found in a different section. Let me check under the CUSTOMERS menu, as that would be the logical place for customer-related functionality including login impersonation logs.

I'll click on the CUSTOMERS menu to expand it and see what options are available there.
